Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-35,0:00:-02.-76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-74,0:00:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fabled Pirate Hunter!\NZoro, the Wandering Swordsman"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to drink up\Nevery bit of liquor in this joint!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, Billy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how many places are you going\Nto ruin before you're satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:20.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yosaku (several years ago)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man over there... has a\Nbounty of 5,000,000 Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5,000,000? What do you say we\Nback off on this one, Yosaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:30.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Johnny (several years ago)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Johnny, if all we do is go after\Nsmall-timers, we won't get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time when a bounty hunter\Nhas to go after the higher ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're saying,\Nbut when it comes to 5,000,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even we would lose by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got any money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not right now. However,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be making some soon enough,\Nonce I cut me up a bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that go unanswered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut you down before you can get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making me exert\Nmyself so much. I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me one thing:\NIs there a bounty on your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be surprised to hear?\NI've got a bounty of 5,000,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say. That's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've earned some money.\NNow give me something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got amazing skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not on the wanted list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's a bounty hunter,\Nsomeone should know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he be the pirate hunter\Nwe've heard about lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard he's one incredibly brutal guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, word is that the pirate\Nhunter uses three swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that one of them is a\Nfamous sword, with a white sheath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, they say\Nhe's like a demon beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's taken the form of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure doesn't look like that.\NIf that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can't just stand by\Nas our prey is taken from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Johnny...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister, if you're a bounty hunter, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you have to abide by our rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't want to make\Nany trouble for the pub,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we were waiting for him to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had first dibs on this guy.\NHe was our prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?! There are\Nrules among fellow bounty hunters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Hawk-Eye Mihawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mihawk? One of the Seven Warlords?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a journey,\Nwith the aim of defeating him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and becoming the world's\Ngreatest swordsmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do collect bounties, in order to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not as though I'm a bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's greatest swordsmaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear that, partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! There's no way!\NYou must be dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, that's what\NI made up my mind to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what anyone else says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was your childhood\Ndream, there's no way you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had claim on him. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can deliver him to the navy.\NThe bounty is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Y-You mean it?!\N--However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my lunch here is on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Johnny! 5,000,000 Berries!\NWe'll be able to eat for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without having to go after any bounties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you become a bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious? So I could eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village where I\Nwas born was really poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, the bandits still\Nhit villages like mine a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they did, the bounty\Nhunters who were after
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bandits' heads came, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down in my heart, I wanted\Nto be just like those dashing men,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who challenged the bandits to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought to myself, someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure do hope that I can take\Ndown those bad men like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't until much later that I learned
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they collected bounties\Nas their profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\NI wanted to be like them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard what that "world's\Ngreatest" dude in there said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it reminded me of myself back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you getting all\Nsentimental on me for? It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandits! The Dick Gang is attacking\Na ranch just outside of town!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dick the Bandit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he is! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a big-leaguer-- 10,000,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap it up, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were hiding quite a bit, huh?\NWe got a big haul today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do we do?\NThey're taking it all away, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about the bandit Dick.\NWe're no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not worth it if he takes\Nour lives from us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, next one!\NTake everything they've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the people in this town?\NThey're such cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they even have\Nthe guts to put up a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe that's smart, in a certain sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who take,\Nand those who get taken from,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're either one or\Nthe other in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being weak is a crime all by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defiance is something only a fool would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there is a fool here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give back our food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something we all\Nworked very hard to store up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got grown-up guts, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry! Stop! You're no match for him! Harry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take it easy, partner.\NEven we would lose to him by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why. He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who I was that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know how to compromise\Nor look out for himself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's me, back when I was still innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:10:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a nameless bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are bounty hunters, huh?\NAre you after my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain. You're just a couple of hyenas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you call us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want money, then I\Ncan give you some charity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't mind small change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We don't want it!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just feel a little bit like\Nbeing champions of justice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Hey, Johnny...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Champions of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey...\N--Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let me be a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johnny...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johnny, you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as\Njustice or evil in this day and age!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mighty prevail!\NThat's all there is to it, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Just this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we turned in a bounty worth\N5,000,000 Berries to the navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy, this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who did in Billy--\Nmy sworn brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:12:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished the\Nsword I asked you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have exceptional skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put in a lot of work. You're too\Nreckless with such a precious sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were an ordinary sword,\Nit would have met the same fate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as those two other broken swords of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get stronger for her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get strong enough\Nthat my name reaches to heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be the world's\Nstrongest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help. I'd like\Nto pay you something extra,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately, right now, I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It's not often\NI get to see such an item as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a feast for the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all like this\Ngood-for-nothing long sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, didn't I tell you so?! Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many swords you carry,\Nit'll never be enough like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I've done it again. Sorry,\NI'll be sure to make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's that punk Dick, the mountain whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a 10,000,000-Berry bandit,\Nwho uses a cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bandit with a price on his head, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. He's too much\Nfor those guys, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two really the ones\Nwho took out my sworn brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! We were the ones who turned in Billy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone else beat him, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you bragging for?\NI thought you were pretty weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you are relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! You want to\Ndie that badly, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! We're done loading\Nall the loot into the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're done? Then let's pull out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sense in messing\Naround with these weaklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said hold it right there, wanted man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've turned in dozens--\Nno, hundreds of bounties by a hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let you get away, it will\Nshame us for generations to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste. It's not worth it, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we won't earn anything... but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are times when a man\Nhas to stick to his beliefs, and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't long for this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew that when we started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, men! Take care of\Nthese guys, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let 'em have it!\N--Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?! Let me go!\NThey're in there fighting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel like fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...think. What can you do\Nwith the power you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, you poor guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a spot on your\Nfaces that hasn't been messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's about time to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't gain me a single\Nred cent to kill the two of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but consider this your own twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hard luck that comes from\Nhaving come after my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But relax, I'll send you into\Nthe next world together, as pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, don't you think?\NThis fight was over a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:17:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, but I'm going\Nto swipe your prey from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come into an urgent\Nneed of money, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A white-sheathed sword...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to borrow your swords for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, but what exactly are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three swords?! You don't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate hunter, Roronoa Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho, so this is the fabled pirate hunter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I've gotten noticeably stronger lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but as soon as I use too\Nmuch of it, my swords break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go overusing my strength so recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the sword,\NI have to get to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where I'm able to get\N100% of its force out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro-san, even using three swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll be able to\Ndefeat that many men at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using three swords is not the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as using the Three-Sword Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style, you say?\NLet's see it, why don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:20:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, don't stand beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to catch\Na cold dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who catch colds are people\Nwho let their mind's guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wonder if someone\Nsomewhere is spreading stories
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about Zoro, the pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never once called myself a pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who did give you\Na name as cool as that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? It doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, crap! My flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni Giri!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that... is the Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, they aren't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm deeply impressed by your skill.\NWould you let us join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are a bounty hunting unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fearsome enough by a hair\Nto silence a crying child,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosaku and Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, Luffy...\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and get off this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's going to\Nbe nothing but trouble here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the same whiff from that\Nold-timer that I do from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then there's nothing\Nto worry about, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's why I'm worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zenny of the Island of Goats and\Nthe Pirate Ship In the Mountains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
